st: of a missionary or evangelist
tb: Almighty and everlasting God, you called your servant N. to preach the Gospel to the people of
    _________ [or to the __________ people]: Raise up in this and every land evangelists and
    heralds of your kingdom, that your Church may proclaim the unsearchable riches of our Savior
    Jesus Christ; who lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit, one God, now and for ever.
    **Amen.**
